restlib

Class Response

  • java.lang.Object
    • restlib.Response
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResponseWrapper

    @Immutable
public abstract class Response
extends Object
    Object representation of an HTTP Response. Implementations must be immutable or effectively immutable.
